description: This file declares functions related to log backup configuration management, including getting and setting boolean and ULONG parameters, validation, commit, rollback, and auxiliary functions for log handling.

methods.name: LogBackup_GetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Retrieves a boolean parameter value for the log backup configuration.

methods.name: LogBackup_SetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Sets a boolean parameter value for the log backup configuration.

methods.name: LogBackup_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves an unsigned long parameter value for the log backup configuration.

methods.name: LogBackup_SetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Sets an unsigned long parameter value for the log backup configuration.

methods.name: LogBackup_Validate
methods.description: Validates the current log backup configuration parameters.

methods.name: LogBackup_Commit
methods.description: Commits changes to the log backup configuration.

methods.name: LogBackup_Rollback
methods.description: Rolls back any uncommitted changes to the log backup configuration.

methods.name: get_logbackupcfg
methods.description: Retrieves the current log backup configuration.
